What are word embedding, some intuition.¶

A technique in natural language processing (NLP) that represents words as vectors in a multi-dimensional space.

  • Boy: [1, 2]
  • Girl: [9, 2]
  • Man: [1,7]

Word Embedding on a network¶

Can we capture the geometry of a network, with a similar representation?¶

Node2Vec: algorithm that generates vector representations of nodes in a graph¶

Aditya Grover, Jure Leskovec node2vec: Scalable Feature Learning for Networks, Proceedings of the 22nd ACM SIGKDD International Conference on Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining, 2016

  • Word embedding on a graph? - borrow the idea of word embedding to networks, to get a numeric representation of a node, captuing the topology of the vicinity of the node.
  • What does it mean? -> capture the whole network topology
  • What can you do with this?
